">PRIMEX PLASTICS Pvt.Ltd.</h1>
<p>
Primex Plastics Pvt. Ltd. stands at the forefront as a premier <a href= https://www.primexplast.com/auto-parts-manufacturer.php><b>Auto Parts Manufacturer</b></a>, specializing in precision Injection and Insert molded components. Our products serve leading OEMs and Tier 1 suppliers across various industries, including Automotive, Electrical, Furniture, White Goods, and more.
</p>

<p>We take pride in our ISO/TS 16949 certification, a testament to our commitment to quality and excellence. Founded and led by seasoned technocrats with over two decades of expertise in Plastics and Sheet Metal component manufacturing, our company combines technical prowess with managerial acumen to deliver superior solutions.</p>

<p>Driven by innovation and dedicated to meeting industry needs, we consistently supply top-tier components that meet stringent standards, ensuring reliability, performance, and satisfaction for our valued clients.</p>

